Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:08.42,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(708.292,834.545)\fade(255,0,255,0,1220,5300,6260)}Guān Yǔ's Three Terms
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:06.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Zhāng Fēi captured Cáo Cāo's General, Liú Dài, at their camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:09.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,However, Liú Bèi feared Cáo Cāo would return,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:12.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,so he released Liú Dài and Wáng Zhōng back to Xǔchang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:17.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, he ordered Guān Yǔ to protect his wives and to remain at Xiàpī.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:21.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sūn Qián and the others guarded Xú Province\Nwhile Zhāng Fēi guarded Xiǎopèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:26.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,They thus formed an ox-horn defense against Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:29.90,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(220.909,705.682)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,2300,2420)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dǒng Chéng's {\i0}servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is Qín Qìngtóng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, I and Dǒng Chéng's concubine were talking in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Chéng saw us, suspected us of an affair, and had me beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:06.74,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(431.591,777.273)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,2540,2860)}Qín Qìngtóng
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even wanted to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I ran away from the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, {\i1}Wáng Zǐfú, Wú Zǐlán, Zhǒng Jí, Wú Shuò, and Mǎ Téng{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,had a secret meeting in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They plan to murder you, sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Chéng had some silk to write characters, but did not know what to use as the pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, Jí Píng and the others bit their fingers to seal their oath with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw them, but couldn't see what they were writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:43.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1262.045,662.727)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1500,1940)}Jí Píng
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor! Chancellor! They had ill intentions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you lie to fulfill your grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare! I wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You said they bit their fingers for an oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Which finger did Jí Píng bite then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The index finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The right index finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, I'm telling the truth! Please see for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this medicine so difficult to decoct?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, this medicine shall remove your ailment in one serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,'Remove my ailment'?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Sir, you are erudite, therefore must know the etiquette!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}I think you should know that \Nwhen the lord needs medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}their vassal must taste it first,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}when the father needs medicine, their son must taste it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}You happen to be one of my aides.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Why did you not taste it first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Medicine is meant for treatment. Why have others taste it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen! This banquet is for you, we end only when drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I invited all the important ministers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.22,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(431.591,777.273)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,2140,2460)}Wáng Zǐfú
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How come Dǒng Chéng isn't here? State Uncle Dǒng?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't arrived yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he fell ill recently and couldn't come because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I heard you, Zǐfú, are a heavy drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! I want to have a drinking contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With your prowess, I cannot possibly beat you, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you refuse merriment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to show an amusement that'd make Zǐfú and the rest of you sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐfú, are you sober?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.02,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(222.955,627.955)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1860,2220)}Dǒng Chéng
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies for being unwelcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, why didn't you come to the banquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was still sick, I dared not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a sickness for our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the State Uncle was ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, I bring to you special medicine to treat thy illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This man has incriminated Wáng Zǐfú \Nand four others. They now imprisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There is but one person not yet found and arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jí Píng?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it that ordered you to poison me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Heaven's will to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, he can't take any more beatings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Jí Píng, why is your right index finger wounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I bit that finger as oath,\Nto kill the traitor of the nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I will have your fingers cut off.\NWe'll see if you can make any more oaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have teeth to bite the traitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and I still have a tongue to curse that traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut his tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,State Uncle, please tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,where is... the imperial palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish... to see it one last time... Before death!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was unable to eliminate the traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus is Heaven's fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Physician!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,State Uncle, perhaps you recognize this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shameless drudge! Lecher! Craven deserter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I should behead you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the first to leak the plot with his testimony. Who dares hurt him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, how could you heed the words of a serf!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Vermin... You would dare?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, the Chancellor has-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Chéng intended to rebel. Was Your Majesty aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuō is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Dǒng{\i1} Zhuō... {\i0}Dǒng {\i1}Chéng!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We... don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget that {\i1}blood edict?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her out. Kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.22,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1620,2020)\pos(147.113,715.909)}Emperor \NXiàn of Hàn
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:14:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Concubine Dǒng is with child of five-months! We beg Chancellor to spare her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And leave a traitorous seed to germinate for vengeance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Guards, take her away! \NIf she refuses to die herself, hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I order Cáo Hóng to lead 3,000 soldiers as\N{\i1}the Imperial Guards{\i0} for the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Henceforth, if any relatives of the Emperor enters the palace without my permission, kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chancellor, we have Dǒng Chéng and over 700 people under arrest! What shall we do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Dǒng Chéng and the others may be dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}but Liú Bèi and Mǎ Téng are also included.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}They must be removed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Mǎ Téng is guarding Xīliáng, not to be trifled with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}We should present him an award to lure him into the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}then eliminate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Liú Bèi has only recently raised his troops, there's still unease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}If you were to march east with a regiment, they will be crushed in one battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent! Send order to all troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby raise a force of 20,000 to attack Xú Province from five directions...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fadeth has the winter, cometh has the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone hither are ice and snow. \NA great time for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gōngyòu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Yuán Shào to convey my greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him to send reinforcments, and return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:38.26,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(243.409,724.091)}Sūn Qián\NStyled: Gōngyòu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything goes wrong, we would have a backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, dividing your troops to guard Xiàpī and Xiǎopèi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,while this forms an ox-horn defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but with the distance between them, if something were to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't say more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, Cáo Cāo is cunning and nefarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With a chance of a raid, you must be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngyòu, you needn't worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:33.06,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(177.955,738.409)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,2060,2380)}Yuán Shào\NStyled: Běnchū
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With Cáo Cāo's attack against Liú Xuándé, Xǔchāng is undefended.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.26,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1223.182,711.818)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,2020,2340)}Tián Fēng\NStyled: Yuánhào
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We should exploit this by moving our troops in,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of rescuing His Majesty, as well as the masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This would also solve Liú Bèi's crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance. \NPlease, my Lord, make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I too know this is most opportune, \Nyet my heart is very confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Raising troops might do no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't miss this opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I could die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, why say such?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have five sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the youngest one I hold dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to him to die from scabies!\NIf he is about to die, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,my mind will be troubled! Troubled so!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We will discuss military affairs later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you return back to Xuándé, explain the matter thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will come to you when I'm feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be easier if Second Brother were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:10.90,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194.318,736.364)\fade(255,0,255,0,540,2820,3260)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled: Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is coming from afar, so they will be exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't be prepared if you raid their camp!\N Their defeat is guaranteed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have always regarded you as a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, you managed to capture Liú Dài with clever planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And your tactic now is textbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! I shall leave to make preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Select elite troops to raid the camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we will raid the camp together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, Cáo Cāo's attack on Xú Province isn't the same as last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This matter is urgent. Sir, hurry back to Xú Province!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I shall take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Sūn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, return to Xú Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There, send someone to hurry over to Xiàpī and inform Yúnchǎng!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This matter is urgent, I will go to Xiàpī myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Yúnchǎng that the enemy is approaching and that he must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Men, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How could the flagpole be broken by wind out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it bode?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, why halt our march?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A great wind broke the flagpole. \NThe Chancellor asks what it could mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the wind come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,From the south-east!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What color was the flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the Chancellor's standard! The flag was red!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.82,0:24:04.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(202.5,699.545)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,6640,6980)}Guō Jiā\NStyled: Fèngxiào
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi will raid us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were my exact thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.94,0:24:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Order all units to standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.74,0:24:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Divide troops into nine! Leave one to build an empty camp! The others shall ambush from all eight sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.13,0:24:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.08,0:24:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heavens smile upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.44,0:24:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.75,0:25:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.53,0:25:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh! We fell into that traitor Cáo's plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.00,0:25:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.17,0:25:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.56,0:25:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Guān Yǔ is protecting Liú Bèi's family. He'll die guarding Xiàpī.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.92,0:25:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't obtain him now, I fear Yuán Shào may.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.90,0:25:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wényuǎn, I have long admired \NYúnchǎng's prowess.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.20,0:25:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to have him for my purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.20,0:25:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be better to pressure him into submission.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.53,0:25:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng is fiercely loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.40,0:25:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng and I are acquaintances. I will persuade him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.50,0:26:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.86,0:26:05.26,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(204.545,699.545)\fade(255,0,255,0,540,1900,2380)}Zhāng Liáo\NStyled: Wényuǎn
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.10,0:26:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.24,0:26:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Yúnchǎng has strength of ten-thousand men,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.48,0:26:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}he can only be swayed by cunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.26,0:26:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}We should send back Liú Bèi's surrendered soldiers back to Xiàpī, and claim that they deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.34,0:26:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Lay ambush within the city, \Nand lure Yúnchǎng out to fight us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.92,0:26:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}I will pretend defeat to lead him somewhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.24,0:26:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}have elite units cut off all escape routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.68,0:26:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Then I will ask for his surrender, and end this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.98,0:26:52.78,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(204.545,699.545)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1420,1780)}Guān Yǔ\NStyled: Yúnchǎng
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.88,0:27:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,General, how can the sky be red today?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.62,0:27:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the beacon from Xiàpī?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.34,0:28:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.40,0:29:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.08,0:29:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.82,0:29:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, do you really want to fight to the death?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.93,0:29:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A warrior without weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.57,0:29:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to mock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.04,0:29:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, then let me tell you of last night's battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.98,0:29:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chancellor was already prepared. He had ambushes on all eight sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.82,0:29:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He has this mountain besieged as of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.90,0:29:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, trying to force your way \Nto Xiàpī simply isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.76,0:29:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Cáo has already broken into the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.52,0:30:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please think this over, Yúnchǎng.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.34,0:30:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wényuǎn, do you intend me to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.21,0:30:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.44,0:30:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, you saved me.\N How could I not repay that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.16,0:30:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then will you break me out of this siege?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.27,0:30:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.38,0:30:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't help me, then why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.12,0:30:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.92,0:30:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no news of sir Xuándé's survival. Sir Yìdé as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.00,0:30:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This time when Chancellor broke\N into the city, we left citizens unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.69,0:30:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chancellor sent someone to watch over sir Xuándé's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.07,0:31:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.85,0:31:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you do wish me to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.19,0:31:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I am at my end, as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.82,0:31:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back whence you came, \Nand we will battle to the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.95,0:31:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.58,0:31:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To answer with such, do you wish ridicule upon yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.75,0:31:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I will die with honor! \NWhy would I be ridiculed?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.79,0:31:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, if you die in battle, \Nyou will have committed three sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.00,0:31:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.10,0:31:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Prior, you and sir Liú formed a bond for greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.26,0:31:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}vowing to share life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.30,0:31:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Now with sir Liú's defeat \Nyou wish to fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.38,0:31:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Yet if your master would return, \Nthere would be no one to aid him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.48,0:31:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Would that not be betrayal to your oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.40,0:31:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}That is your first sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.14,0:31:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Sir Liú has entrusted his family to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.26,0:32:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}If you die now, his wives would be without support!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.64,0:32:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}How could that not betray his trust in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.04,0:32:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}That is your second sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.04,0:32:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}You abilities are without peer, and your learning vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.60,0:32:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Yet you don't consider aiding sir Liú to restore the Hàn Empire, but recklessly tread on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.88,0:32:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}That is a fool's bravery! How is that virtuous?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.52,0:32:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}That is your third sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.64,0:32:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}These are your three sins. I am sorry to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.16,0:32:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}You say there are three sins, \Nthen what do you wish of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.35,0:32:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Lord Cáo has us surrounded on all sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.65,0:32:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}If you don't surrender, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.48,0:32:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}To die would be for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.76,0:32:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Better to surrender to Lord Cáo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.80,0:33:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}There, you could wait for news of your master, then return to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.68,0:33:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}You would protect the two mistresses,\Nand secondly, you would not betray your oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.08,0:33:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Third, you could exercise aid for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.14,0:33:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}With these three reasons, please reconsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.97,0:33:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}For your three reasons, I answer with three terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.20,0:33:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}If Lord Cáo is able to heed it, I shall cast off my armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.30,0:33:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}If he won't accept it, I would rather die in battle with my three sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.64,0:33:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}The Chancellor is bounteous. How could he refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.12,0:33:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}He will listen to your three conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.00,0:34:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}First, me and the Imperial Uncle made an oath to restore the Hàn Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.08,0:34:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}I cede only to the Emperor, not to Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.98,0:34:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Second, my sisters-in-laws' residence shall be supported with their husband's imperial salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.00,0:34:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Everyone, regardless of rank, is not allowed to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.76,0:34:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}Third, once I find out \Nthe Imperial Uncle's whereabouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.64,0:34:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}be the distance a thousand or tenfold,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.94,0:34:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}I will leave sir Cáo to search for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.56,0:34:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}If one of these three is refused, I will never surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.58,0:34:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,884.221)}I expect you, Wényuǎn, to report this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.38,0:35:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He would leave once he finds out where Liú Bèi is?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.12,0:35:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why even bother keeping Guān Yúnchǎng?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.22,0:35:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, you don't need to worry.\NYúncháng relation to Liú Bèi is only of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.20,0:35:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But if Chancellor were to show more favor to Yúncháng, to win him over,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.76,0:35:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,why worry of Yúncháng's stay then?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.47,0:35:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, is it not for Yúncháng's loyalty that you admire him of?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.92,0:35:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He is an honorable man who will repay his dues.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.70,0:35:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are correct, Wényuǎn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.79,0:35:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! I accept his three conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.02,0:35:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.62,0:35:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.47,0:36:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All troops surrounding the mountain are to retreat 3,000 lǐ.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.31,0:36:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow Yúnchǎng to enter the city \Nand meet with two mistresses first.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.09,0:36:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.47,0:36:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.88,0:36:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me for my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.88,0:36:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the city to fight, \Nbut was besieged at the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.22,0:37:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo sent Zhāng Liáo to persuade my surrender. I accepted for three conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.36,0:37:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I concede to the Hàn Empire, not to Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.89,0:37:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Secondly, he is to support the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.59,0:37:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your residence cannot be entered by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.31,0:37:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Third, once I discover my elder brother's whereabouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.62,0:37:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will leave Cáo Cāo to find him, no matter the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.56,0:37:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not ask of your thoughts, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.20,0:37:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother, do you know where the Imperial Uncle is?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.83,0:37:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.70,0:37:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, when the Cáo army \Nentered the city, we would've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.85,0:37:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet no one had intruded us, \Nnot one soldier dared to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.75,0:38:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've sealed your agreement, why discuss it with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.53,0:38:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I only fear that in the future, that Cáo Cāo won't allow you to search for the imperial uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.11,0:38:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, sisters-in-law. \NI made sure to have my say in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.60,0:38:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you can make the decisions. \NYou don't need to discuss them with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.85,0:38:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Second Brother, be on your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.60,0:38:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisters-in-laws, please come in and rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.34,0:39:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This defeated warrior is grateful\N for the Chancellor's mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.56,0:39:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long admired your loyalty and integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.69,0:39:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To meet with you today is my greatest fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.36,0:39:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chancellor, Wényuǎn received my three terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.17,0:40:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chancellor, I hope you won't violate your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.94,0:40:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I made my promise.\NHow could I dare violate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.16,0:40:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If I know the imperial uncle's location,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.44,0:40:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will search for him by hook or by crook.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.19,0:40:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I might not bid you farewell then. \NPlease accept my discourtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.70,0:40:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where Xuándé is at is where I will send you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.84,0:40:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I only fear he may have already\N died within my army's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.92,0:40:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, fear not, for I will search everywhere for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.16,0:40:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chancellor!
